Tabula Muris 10x data

TabulaMurisDroplet.Rd

UMI counts from the 10x (droplet) single-cell RNA-seq data collected by the Tabula Muris Consortium. The object contains counts for 23,341 genes in 70,118 cells.

TabulaMurisDroplet(metadata = FALSE)

Arguments

metadata

Logical, whether only metadata should be returned

Format

SingleCellExperiment

Value

Returns a SingleCellExperiment object.

Author

Charlotte Soneson

References

The Tabula Muris Consortium: Single-cell transcriptomics of 20 mouse organs creates a Tabula Muris. Nature doi:10.1038/s41586-018-0590-4 (2018).

Examples

    TabulaMurisDroplet(metadata = FALSE)
